# Day teaching primer (kids_math)

## When this applies

- Adding or editing **`teachingSummary` / `teachingSteps`** on a **`DayConcept`** (Grade A/B content under `lib/content/grade-*`).
- Changing **`DayTeachingPrimer`** or day-hub layout.

## UI modules

- `components/DayTeachingPrimer.tsx` — re-exports `DayTeachingPrimer` (stable import path).
- `components/teaching-primer/DayTeachingPrimer.tsx` — hub panel + collapse + TTS wiring.
- `components/teaching-primer/TeachingPrimerExpandedContent.tsx` — summary + ordered steps.
- `components/teaching-primer/TeachingPrimerExpandToggle.tsx` — expand/collapse control.

## Authoring

- **Hebrew only** in content fields; keep tone low-pressure and child-friendly.
- **Align** with the day's section **`WorkedExample`** — no contradictory definitions vs. arithmetic/geometry prompts.
- **Length:** aim short; very long text triggers **collapse** on the hub (`DAY_PRIMER_COLLAPSE_CHAR_THRESHOLD` in `lib/content/buildDayPrimerSpeakText.ts`, or **>4** steps).
- **Optional:** omit both fields → **no** primer panel (empty state).

## TTS

- **No autoplay.** Uses `TapToPlayTtsButton` + admin **TTS** preference (`kids_math.admin_prefs.v1`).
- Speak text = `buildDayPrimerSpeakText(day)` (summary + steps, joined for synthesis).

## Test IDs

- Tier-1: `testIds.screen.dayOverview.teachingPrimer(grade, dayId)` on the `Surface` root.
- Nested: `childTid(primerRoot, "topRow" | "title" | "body" | "summary" | "steps" | "step", idx | "preview")`.
- TTS: `testIds.screen.dayOverview.teachingPrimerTts(grade, dayId)`.
- Expand: `testIds.screen.dayOverview.teachingPrimerExpand(grade, dayId)`.

## Quality

- Extend **`tests/unit/lib/content/content-validity.test.ts`** if adding new content constraints.
- E2E coverage: **`tests/e2e/day-smoke.spec.ts`** (primer visible / absent / TTS).

See also **`AGENTS.md`** (MoE alignment for curricular claims) and **`build-school-year.mdc`** for year-scale content workflow.
